    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We shouldn't polyfill, but instead use our own util function which uses indexOf. The real polyfill on MDN seems more advanced, but not things we really need: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/find#Polyfill (it also has a note about not polyfilling)",
    "created_at": "2019-04-24T13:29:05Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/3706#issuecomment-486229454",
